race.comment: COCHISE ATTITUDE (2) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 3 last run (30.57) at this track. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from 10 starts. Can find winning form. TRICKY MICKY (4) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 5 last run (30.82) at this track. Has a strong record from box 4, including three wins. Can measure up. TAGOVAILOA (6) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 5.5 lengths second behind Goldstar Sandler in 30.63. Bold showing expected again. CLEAN CUT (1) hit the frame latest (25.52) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has four wins already from this draw.
